headline: Cessna SkyCourier Expands Global Reach With Two Aircraft Order From AIR Marshall Islands
summary: WICHITA, Kan., November 22, 2024--Textron Aviation, a Textron Inc. (NYSE:TXT) company, today announced a two-aircraft purchase agreement with AIR Marshall Islands Inc. (AMI) for its twin-engine, large-utility turboprop, the Cessna SkyCourier. The two aircraft – both passenger variants - will be used to support travel throughout the communities within the Marshall Islands.
